// Managed by Ansible (roles/agent_lxc). Keep in sync with the MacBook-side
// .stignore in ~/projects/syncthing/agent-lxc/<folder>/.stignore — mismatched
// ignores cause "directory has been deleted on a remote device but is not
// empty" warnings.
// (?d) lets Syncthing delete these items when removing a parent directory.
(?d).DS_Store
(?d)node_modules
(?d).venv
(?d)__pycache__
